---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Terms of Service - How I Claude Code" description="Terms of service for How I Claude Code - license to host, responsibilities, and liability.">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8 max-w-3xl">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Terms of Service</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-lg">
      <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-6">Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString()}</p>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">1. License to Host</h2>
        <p>
          By uploading content to How I Claude Code, you grant us a <strong>non-exclusive license</strong> to host and display your public or unlisted content. You retain all rights to your content and can delete it at any time. We will purge caches within a reasonable timeframe after deletion.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">2. Your Responsibilities</h2>
        <p>You warrant that:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>You have the right to publish the content (code and text)</li>
          <li>You have removed or will redact any secrets and personal data before making content public</li>
          <li>You will not upload unlawful content or content that violates others' rights</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">3. Aggregate Statistics</h2>
        <p>
          We may show <strong>aggregate statistics</strong> about public content (e.g., trending tags, popular topics). We do not sell identifiable data or track individuals across sites.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">4. DMCA & Takedown</h2>
        <p>
          If you believe content infringes your rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:dmca@howi.cc">dmca@howi.cc</a> with:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Your contact information</li>
          <li>Description of the infringing content</li>
          <li>URL of the content</li>
          <li>Statement of good faith belief</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">5. Liability & Warranty</h2>
        <p>
          How I Claude Code is provided "as is" without warranty. We are not liable for damages arising from use of the service. We reserve the right to remove content that violates these terms.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">6. Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p>
          We may update these terms. Continued use after changes constitutes acceptance. We will notify users of material changes.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
